caption:
Say goodbye to benzoyl peroxide and hello to gentler, more effective alternatives for clear skin! 🌿 

Our acne-fighting formulas are powered by salicylic acid, azelaic acid, glycolic acid, sulfur, niacinamide, natural extracts of thyme, oregano, green tea + willow bark, and gluconolactone — part science/part nature ingredient blends that target breakouts without compromising your skin's health. No dryness, no irritation, just clear, balanced skin.
